node.text:
✨🤌💖🇮🇹ITALIAN MOMENT🇮🇹🤌✨💖
*english below

Dato che nei Paesi Bassi le tende sono un optional ed i muri sono di cartone, sono abbastanza sicura che i miei vicini, nell'ultima settimana, abbiano cercato più volte su google il signor Enzino, le tic tac, gli angioletti Thun e le nutrie.
Questo perché io e Patrik (da bravi padovani doc) abbiamo fatto una mega maratona di Rubrichette ed abbiamo visto TUTTE le puntate, alcune pure più volte!
Io non sono brava a dire a parole quanto mi abbia riportato il sorriso in un periodo stressante questa cosa, quindi ho fatto un fumettino!
Grazie per accendere il ritmo della vita, piccole tic tac! Baci stellari!💖
______________________
I'm sorry, i know many of you don't speak Italian and you cannot understand all the pop culture references in their videos, but these two run one of my favorite YouTube channels so i made this!
We're even from the same city so the relatability goes through the roof! I hope you'll still like it and if you miss comics go check the latest one I posted yesterday if you haven't already!:) 💖
#procreate #drawing #illustration #art #webcomic #instacomics #digitalart #fumetti #rubrichette✨ #rubrichette #gabriella #spettinata

node.text:
I never really believed in marriage but i had this dream where one of my best friends was walking me down the aisle (of a town hall or something, not a church ahah) instead of my father and I thought it was cute!
I guess all the tension building up in the days before meeting my father after many years brought to this. He was a total disappointment but I’m happy i have such good friends in my life that don’t make me think i had kind of a s*itty family!

Sometimes i think of faking a marriage one day. Like doing everything, party, food, drinks, dancing but no actual piece of paper signed in the end. Just to invite whoever i want and have a big party with people i love 😂
#friends #friend #bff #friendship #married #marriage #gettingmarried #art #drawing #illustration #procreate #comics #webcomic #instacomic #digitalart

node.text:
I may not have talked much about it but my view on kinks is pretty open. Until you’re not hurting anyone and your partners are consenting adults that know what’s going on, go for it.
A couple people told me they look at my pole dance pics for feet content and I honestly wouldn’t post it if i felt uncomfortable about it.
I understand this is not everyone’s view on it, I’m just sharing mine!

Some of my exes pressured me into s€x when I didn’t want to, or did things they knew I didn’t like just hoping i was too shy to speak up, years later i had some of the most honest conversations about my s€x life with my current boyfriend and people I didn’t even know at underground (but legal lol) parties, that were either s€x workers or bd$m fans.

Just be nice with people that aren’t doing anything wrong to you and just live their life in a different way. You don’t have to understand, like or share their views on life but just respect your differences! ❤️

Also Keanu Reeves.
In doubt be like him.

#comics #webcomic #funny #art #drawing #illustration #instacomic #procreate #mentalhealth #kinkymemes #kinky #freedom #benice #keanureeves #justbeniceok

node.text:
Lately I noticed that my silly stories where i pose all sexy and then make a stupid face and show how the belly rolls up when I’m not posing, get quite a positive response and some of you find them helpful in finding their own confidence. I started saving them in the highlights!:)
__
I spent so much time hating my body and obsessing over things the internet and society in general made me hate but that, before being influenced, I didn’t care about.
I’m healthy, i found a way to exercise that i also like as an activity and it’s not just me forcing myself to work out to be skinnier. Now i want to be stronger and healthier!
This is absolutely not a encouragement to not improve yourself if you feel like to, but more a reminder that so many of us, regardless of gender, age or anything, are too hard on themselves.
It’s not like for me it’s all easy, it took a long time and a lot of work on myself to get here, so don’t get discouraged and try to love yourself and your body in the process!
#selflove #love #mentalhealth #health #workout #stronger #loveyourself #bodypositivity #art #comics #illustration #webcomic #instacomic #procreate #digitalart

node.text:
I will never step on every square foot of this planet. I will probably never see this stranger i talked to for 5 minutes at the supermarket ever again. I will never eat this very slice of pizza ever again.
Idk…sometimes i stress about completely useless stuff, but the fact that it’s a “never in your life” gives me anxiety.

node.text:
As you might have noticed if you watched my stories in the past two days, I’m finally in Italy to see my mom and some friends!:)
I’ll be here for three weeks and I’ll try to spend as much time as possible with loved ones. Just a heads up, this doesn’t mean no comics for almost a month but they might be less than usual.
We got here with a night train just a few hours after we tested negative to covid and got our first vaccine shot but we will still be careful with who we meet and how we meet them and keep on wearing a mask. Please be safe if you travel and, if you can, wait if your government advises agains it!
I’m off to eat a very Italian pizza, with my very Italian mom and boyfriend and I’m very happy! 🤌💖✨
#comics #webcomic #art #drawing #mom #momma #family #italy #mamma #mum #travel #love #procreate #digitalart #happy

I was also able to understand and talk to him in Dutch so i was extra happy!
Honestly I really appreciate guys that just genuinely compliment you and then make their intentions clear, asking if you jave a boyfriend almost right away. I said yes, he wished me a nice evening and we said bye. :)
